headline.0: 8 Quirky Things Millennial Men Will Try to Better Themselves in 2014

short_description.0: Men do try to better themselves as part of their New Year's resolutions and to learn the latest ways I've consulted AskMen editors who provided some wacky, innovative, and clever methods from their annual 12 Days To Be A Better Man series.
